                <h2 class="cd-title">web design/ux principles</h2>

                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Use clear messaging</strong> to guide the user. All buttons, links, and calls to action should have descriptive text which communicate our personality and tone of voice.</li>
                    <li><strong>Use white space</strong> to break up sections of the page instead of hard lines. Alternatively, use differently coloured page sections.</li>
                    <li><strong>Use product photography freely</strong>. We're proud of our products and like to show them off with high quality photography.</li>
                    <li><strong>No gimmicks</strong>. We stick with what works best and prefer to use conventional patterns rather then re-invent the wheel. We want websites everybody can use without a learning curve.</li>
